      "Phase 4: Smart-α participation → stochastic DC-OPF summary\n",
      "============================================================\n",
      "\n",
      "Participation scalar α:\n",
      "  Mean α used:                 0.9981\n",
      "  Std α used:                  0.0074\n",
      "  Min / Max:               0.9460 / 1.0058\n",
      "\n",
      "Forecast quality (unscaled PGBM forecast):\n",
      "  MAE:                           10.9 MW\n",
      "  Bias:                           1.3 MW\n",
      "\n",
      "Cost outputs:\n",
      "  E[SP expected cost]:     $  118,063.25/hr\n",
      "  E[realized cost]:        $   95,678.52/hr\n",
      "  Calibration gap:         $  -22,384.73/hr\n",
      "\n",
      "Realized performance:\n",
      "  Avg load shed:                 0.26 MW\n",
      "  Avg limit violation:           0.22 MW\n"
     ]
    },
